I also like... music.

115
00:05:06,607 --> 00:05:09,553
And I think we're
going to go out again.

116
00:05:09,567 --> 00:05:12,132
- Dude, you gotta ditch her.
- Obviously.

117
00:05:12,596 --> 00:05:13,522
