I met a girl at this very bar.

138
00:06:01,578 --> 00:06:04,650
I saw that she had
the crazy eyes...

139
00:06:06,557 --> 00:06:07,830
...but I ignored it.

140
00:06:07,845 --> 00:06:10,181
And then, sure enough.

141
00:06:10,846 --> 00:06:12,920
Barney, can I ask
you a question?

142
00:06:12,935 --> 00:06:14,411
Anything.

143
00:06:14,766 --> 00:06:17,430
Would you like to
have a threesome?

144
00:06:17,773 --> 00:06:19,081
Of course.

145
00:06:19,097 --> 00:06:21,853
Great. It'll be you,
me and Mr. Weasels.

146
00:06:24,099 --> 00:06:25,702
So, did you do it?

147
00:06:25,719 --> 00:06:28,211
No. It ended up
being just a twosome

148
00:06:28,225 --> 00:06:30,580
with the third one
watching from a chair.

149
00:06:31,016 --> 00:06:32,622
Which one were you?

150
00:06:33,447 --> 00:06:35,202
I'd rather not say.

151
00:06:35,516 --> 00:06:38,062
Look, there was a time I didn't
believe in the crazy eyes either,

152
00:06:38,096 --> 00:06:40,012
and then I met Jeanine.

153
00:06:40,078 --> 00:06:42,771
She had serious crazy eyes.

154
00:06:43,228 --> 00:06:46,660
