just imagining it, but then...

155
00:06:46,675 --> 00:06:48,440
So, should we go get a drink?

156
00:06:48,458 --> 00:06:50,860
As long as it's in
your apartment.

157
00:06:52,125 --> 00:06:53,183
Whoa, I'm sorry.

158
00:06:53,195 --> 00:06:58,103
