comes bubbling to the surface.

166
00:07:16,197 --> 00:07:16,982
Hello?

167
00:07:16,998 --> 00:07:18,622
Marshall, it's Chloe.

168
00:07:18,638 --> 00:07:21,232
Are you the one who's
called me like nine times?

169
00:07:21,248 --> 00:07:23,342
Yeah. Could you come get me?

170
00:07:23,355 --> 00:07:25,803
I'm in the middle
of taking a test.

171
00:07:25,818 --> 00:07:27,770
Please. I'm so scared.

172
00:07:28,017 --> 00:07:29,433
