175
00:07:32,668 --> 00:07:34,890
and he had a limp and
a big hump on his back

176
00:07:34,908 --> 00:07:36,302
and the police
didn't believe me

177
00:07:36,315 --> 00:07:39,150
and I almost got trampled
by a horse and...

178
