God I must sound totally
crazy to you right now.

179
00:07:42,655 --> 00:07:45,010
No. Pfft.

180
00:07:45,027 --> 00:07:46,302
Not at all.

181
00:07:46,927 --> 00:07:48,652
So, she's needy crazy.

182
00:07:48,668 --> 00:07:50,440
That's one of the worst kinds.

183
00:07:50,457 --> 00:07:51,761
