192
00:08:11,617 --> 00:08:14,313
Ned. I told you
to call him Ned.

193
00:08:14,466 --> 00:08:16,322
That's just sad.

194
00:08:16,335 --> 00:08:18,103
Sorry, Swarley.

195
00:08:19,357 --> 00:08:21,833
So, do just you
and Ted live here

196
00:08:21,848 --> 00:08:23,613
