199
00:08:30,955 --> 00:08:32,673
Oh, I, uh, dropped my keys.

200
00:08:34,835 --> 00:08:36,561
So, here you go.

201
00:08:36,576 --> 00:08:39,012
Two pumpkin beers.

202
00:08:39,168 --> 00:08:41,880
