nice time tonight.

215
00:09:21,315 --> 00:09:23,592
Yeah, me, too. Stop blinking.

216
00:09:23,928 --> 00:09:27,372
I like your eyes a lot, too.

217
00:09:29,376 --> 00:09:30,640
Stop!

218
00:09:34,208 --> 00:09:36,891
Hi. I'm Lily.

219
00:09:40,178 --> 00:09:42,122
