220
00:09:42,136 --> 00:09:44,220
Now, kids,
I know Lily hiding in the apartment

221
00:09:44,235 --> 00:09:47,520
while Marshall was on a date with
another girl seems pretty crazy,

222
00:09:47,538 --> 00:09:49,880
but when you hear her
side of the story,

223
00:09:49,897 --> 00:09:51,950
well, it's still pretty crazy.

224
00:09:52,627 --> 00:09:54,180
