225
00:09:54,196 --> 00:09:56,402
No. Okay? No. No more.

226
00:09:56,418 --> 00:09:58,473
I will not let this 
become a thing. It's over.

227
00:09:58,487 --> 00:10:00,450
No more Swarley. No Swarlz.

228
00:10:00,466 --> 00:10:02,942
No more Swar-lay.

229
00:10:02,957 --> 00:10:05,920
No more Swar...
wait for it... ley.

230
00:10:05,938 --> 00:10:08,510
No more Bob Swarley, mon.

231
00:10:08,526 --> 00:10:11,471
No more. No! It's over.

232
00:10:11,485 --> 00:10:13,061
Do you understand?

233
00:10:13,078 --> 00:10:13,903
